==English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|condempnen}}, from {{der|en|fro|condamner}}, from {{der|en|la|condemnāre||to sentence, condemn, blame}}, from {{m|la|com-}} + {{m|la|damnāre||to harm, condemn, damn}}, from {{m|la|damnum||damage, injury, loss}}. Displaced {{cog|enm|fordemen, fordemen|part}} (from {{cog|ang|fordeman|condemn, sentence, doom}} > Modern English {{m|en|fordeem}}

